Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the tears is a beckoning cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can this cat also beckon crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which hand is raised?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.22,0:00:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The left hand? The right hand? Or even both hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely no looking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I wouldn't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.93,0:02:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get it over with already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did I, who just happened to be passing\Nby, have to get roped into doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because Edogawa-kun is shorter than we need him to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm only like this thanks to a certain someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where this kitten is from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does anyone know this cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cha-Cha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Cha-Cha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for startling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,See, this is my cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:01.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She disappeared a while ago I've been looking for her ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:59.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fs12\blur2}Ishigami Tomatsu (35)\NCafe Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she hurt her right paw, since it was bleeding a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you bandaged her up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To show my gratitude, won't you join\Nme in my shop and have a cold drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a lively customer here at the moment, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.04,0:03:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whip, the whip! Use the whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something terrible has happened, come quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanemaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Master, coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another cup of coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a stroll and saw the patrol cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wondered if I might be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a case?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Office Kanemaru"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What sort of business does this company currently conduct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just acts important by using a foreign name, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All he really does is issue high-interest loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even though he's the president of the\Ncompany, there aren't any other employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's name and family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanemaru Kenzou-san, age 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was single with no family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the coroner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was a blow\Nto the head by a blunt object.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was probably one of the beckoning cats in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, there are a lot of pieces here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The broken pieces lying around the victim's body are likely from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was a beckoning cat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about the estimated time of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time of death was a few hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was sometime between 11:00 AM and 1:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's that detective, Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This lady was the first to discover the body, Imaoka Fumie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She comes here once a week to clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:54.65,Signs,,0,0,0,,Imoka Fumie (65)\NJanitor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:06:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, she arrived at her usual time of approximately 1:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who are you reporting to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the safe has been opened as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The safe contained nearly a million yen in cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't seem to have been disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who first discovered the body is, in fact, the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Imaoka-san here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She owed the victim 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably underwent a harsh collection\Nprocess, and not knowing what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This happens all too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're suspecting me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that I borrowed 300,000 from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he said he would ignore the interest on\Nthe loan if I came here to clean once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now—there's no reason to get so agitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this on the president's desk in the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd have a look at it please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a memo of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,September 3rd, 12:30 PM—Murai Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim, Kanemaru-san, had plans to meet with this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The master of the cafe across the street, Ishigami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Claimed to have spotted a young woman\Napproaching the office around 12:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A young woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what'd she look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:47.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She was dressed quite glamorously, wearing\Ndesigner brand clothes and a shoulder bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Murai Chika (22)\NMotojo University Student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, after only about ten minutes, she ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she arrived at 12:30, she must have left at 12:40.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of which happen to fit the estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have already ordered a search party...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And provided them with the description given here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak with her directly, so bring her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've found a woman who appears to be Murai Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're headed here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the victim, Kanemaru-san, sure has a weird hobby, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Collecting beckoning cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Kanemaru-san, it wasn't a hobby, it was pure greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He collected them because he liked money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He collected them out of greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see, all of the cats lined up\Nhere have only their right paw raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I asked why none had their left paws raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:09:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it's because the cats with their\Nleft paws raised beckon customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the ones with their right paws raised beckon wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as I have money, it doesn't matter if no customers come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be wasteful to spend money on tea for them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He simply felt that money was the most important thing in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the cat's raised right paw brings in wealth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You ever heard anything about a cat beckoning wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, even though I won't have to come here and clean anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll kind of miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Kanemaru-san ever use the vacuum cleaner himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said it'd waste money on electricity,\Nso he only got me to do it once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't wander around and get in the way of the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dust bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't throw it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's no reason why Kanemaru-san, who\Ndidn't clean, would throw it away—how strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake, it was that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what was the vacuum cleaner used for here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why was the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What purpose would be served by removing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the lending agreement she'd taken found on\Nher and the appointment memo, she can't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I wasn't needed for this one after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like a beckoning cat's paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was under the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably flew here from the force of the blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a flip clock, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The panels flip as the time changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To still be using something as unusual as this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as Imaoka-san said, he was a pretty weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This piece flew all the way over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I can't rule out that possibility completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This didn't fly here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,\NI see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why they used the vacuum cleaner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's confessed to her crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that, in order to buy all her brand-name\Nclothes, shoes, accessories, bags, and watches...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She accumulated a sizable debt with Kanemaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even quit college and started a\Npart-time job, but it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why today, she finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,¥100,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not even enough to cover the interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the limit of my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just ask your parents in the countryside to cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, don't tell my parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this for free, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't bring all of the money by tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then she grabbed the lending agreement and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is... {\alpha&FF&\t(1400,1401,\alpha&00&}blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something happened in this room, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1/60th of the evidence exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1/60th of the evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "once-an-hour" evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something I have to do, so I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you, wielding the beckoning cat,\Nproceeded in the direction of the safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And swung downward, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't that simple of a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like his paw has stopped bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it'd be best if you had a veterinarian take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Conan, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we still have ten minutes before the last race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I watch it back at your cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it came, and that we've got the culprit wrong again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's exactly it, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murai Chika-san did indeed strike\NKanemaru-san with a beckoning cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in this very office.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But her crime is merely assault, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having been struck by Chika-san,\NKanemaru-san likely lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not long afterward...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At around 12:40 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san witnessed the fleeing Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minutes later...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanemaru-san was struck once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying he was attacked twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would, please bring out the clock from the president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hirota-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please turn the time back to 12:59 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a unique retro clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, you just do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is—!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood that flew from Kanemaru-san's head when he was struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it happened in the president's office in the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time was 12:59 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, she had already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone else attacked Kanemaru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and that person was the\None who killed Kanemaru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying the President's office\Nwas the scene of the second attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit tried to clean up the blood stains, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the clock's dial had changed during that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit didn't notice that any blood had sprayed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who is the murderer we're dealing with here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please look at the notepad over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanemaru-san left a clue for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,12:30 PM—Murai Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the next page, under that memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blank page.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was once there was likely a memo detailing a meeting\Ntime around that of Chika-san's but with the culprit's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Realizing this, the murderer removed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please shade the page using a pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A faint impression from the writing should still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some characters have appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,September 3rd, 1:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you scheduled to meet with Kanemaru-san at 1:00 PM today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had scheduled to meet with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:07.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it was very busy in the shop, so I couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give that thing to the inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is... blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the pawprint from Cha-Cha, whose front paw was injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pawprint on the window of the president's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should be the same as the one on that handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please confirm this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san said that he hadn't come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Cha-Cha did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's unimaginable that a kitten opened the door and came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window was open, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a crime-prevention lattice, so even\Na cat couldn't jump in from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you said, Detective Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pawprints match perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which leaves us with one possibility:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cha-Cha came here with Ishigami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san, you came here at 1:00 PM as promised on\Nthe memo and met with Kanemaru-san, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, under the sofa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a beckoning cat fragment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is a fragment of the weapon\NIshigami-san struck Kanemaru-san with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:30.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Mouri-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she struck him with a beckoning cat that was on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's most likely the one missing from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one cat's worth of shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where would you say the beckoning cat that Ishigami-san used is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That beckoning cat fragment is the left paw, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:19:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the cats here are ones with their right paws raised, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their left paw is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fragment came from another beckoning\Ncat that didn't belong to this collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying another kind of beckoning\Ncat was brought in from outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought a beckoning cat with its left paw raised, and\Ncame here a little before the 1:00 PM appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was when you saw Chika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanemaru-san, who had been struck by Chika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only lost consciousness, and woke up soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanemaru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of not returning the money, that woman suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do you have the money ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:20:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I got you this, to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a beckoning cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones I collect are money-beckoning\Ncats with their right paws raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the left paw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want this rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go back to your shop and prepare to vacate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and that woman are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of idiot does he think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Startled at the situation, Cha-Cha injured her paw...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, frightened, escaped out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, you decided to frame Chika-san for the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And dragged Kanemaru-san's body out into the main room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then looked around for any blood\Nsplatters and cleaned them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Collected the large fragments, and used the\Nvacuum cleaner to collect the small ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, along with the dust bag, you took them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, a few pieces of evidence were left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ishigami-san, what do you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not that much time has passed since the crime occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your means of escape are limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be difficult for us to locate the fragments of the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, all we'd have to do is match the\Nfingerprints and blood to reveal everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happened just as Detective Mouri described it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since I wasn't able to repay the money today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was going to take my shop away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beckoning cats are supposed to bring good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only this time, it was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here we are, perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look, a beckoning cat made by yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.14,0:23:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beckoning both money and clients, it raises both paws.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Banzai"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hits it right on the mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks more like it's giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of a famous mystery author was discovered in a villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his finger, a ring that had been put on upside-down...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both Detective Satou and Detective Takagi rushed to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Detective Satou's finger was also a mysterious ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.34,0:24:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unsolved mysteries of both the case and love!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.14,0:24:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Detective Takagi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.56,0:24:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tightrope Walking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.16,0:24:52.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,No more beckoning cats for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.19,0:24:52.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:54.66,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Because you only beckon cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:54.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
